      <title>碳排放量猛增 30%，微软的 AI 推动危及气候目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/microsoft-s-ai-investment-imperils-climate-goal-as-emissions-jump-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该公司到 2030 年实现碳负排放的目标较难实现，但总裁布拉德·史密斯 (Brad Smith) 表示，人工智能为世界带来的好处将超过其对环境的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/microsoft-s-ai-investment-imperils-climate-goal-as-emissions-jump-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 16:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
